{"tid":552901,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩打電話叫麥麥送","createTime":"2018-02-07T03:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T14:03:25.000Z","uid":162984,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f64c4e3de521b875eddee1e5e85aaea99d2b7272","tid":552901,"uid":162984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"成兩年冇叫過麥麥送 岩岩一訓醒家姐話想食 咁咪打電話叫囉<br />\n問完落單電話 問埋姓咩 都冇咩事 <br />\n之後聽電話個姐姐講佐兩個地址 問我送邊個<br />\n一個係我舊地址 一個係拍佐五年拖既ex地址<br />\n果下個心酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢分佐手差唔多兩年 所有野都唔同哂 <br />\n以前兩個人住得近 成日係對方屋企打機睇片 肚餓就叫外賣<br />\n而家分佐手 我屋都搬埋 兩個人已經係兩個世界<br />\n原本以為自己一早放低哂 但原來一個咁普通既問題 問你外賣送邊 都可以諗起咁多回憶 唉"},{"pid":"7e6231f7681005633e9fb918fedf993bf0bb9238","tid":552901,"uid":71237,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"試下幫對方叫外賣"},{"pid":"6e20ec666c7ace8e26837744e6c6d0b2c19b9817","tid":552901,"uid":129660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"好彩我未拍過拖姐"},{"pid":"9ec7df86c09f6fe9944e16adb192ab5793da3cb3","tid":552901,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:37:26.000Z","msg":"乜重有人唔係上網叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d9c8a62ec3f543c724748c83189a672680bd55","tid":552901,"uid":162984,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜重有人唔係上網叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慣佐上網睇完食咩 之後打電話叫"},{"pid":"d740398a54f27e5ceb4a08e31b63492afd92fa57","tid":552901,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T07:48:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c94dd5d05ea93e45d4cf849b95bbe8eed7166134","tid":552901,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}